content: 广州32岁的杨吃货昨日早晨7点24分抢救无效死于休克,全身皮肤呈黑紫色.州医三院神经内科医生康博士告诉记者,这是肺鼠疫,死亡率非常高.医生断定这是杨姐昨日吃猫引起的,但家属称他们吃的猫绝无鼠疫症状,为此记者请教了传染病教授陈菊梅.原来,猫自身有抗鼠疫的免疫故不易被感染,但鼠疫杆菌会残留在体内.

content_en: Yang Shuhuo, 32, of Guangzhou, died of shock at 7:24 am yesterday, with dark purple skin all over his body. State hospital neurology doctor Kang told reporters, this is pneumonic plague, mortality is very high. The doctor concluded that this was caused by Yang Jie eating cats yesterday, but the family said that the cats they ate had no symptoms of plague, so the reporter consulted Chen Jumei, a professor of infectious diseases. It turns out that cats have their own immunity to plague, which makes them less susceptible to infection, but yersinia pestis remains in their bodies.

content: 【自制无毒驱蚊水 家长必备啊】市面上的驱蚊水、驱蚊花露水中含有避蚊胺（一种农药成分的化工原料），不适合婴幼儿使用。推荐一招自制无毒驱蚊水的方法:准备一可喷水的小瓶,五片复合维生素B。将矿泉水灌入小瓶后放进药片摇匀,将小瓶对准身体喷一下即可,因为蚊子害怕复合维生素B的味道。

One way to make your own non-toxic mosquito repellent is to prepare a spray vial with five B vitamin complex tablets. content: 【世界卫生组织证实刚果伊波拉病毒已失控扩散】世界卫生组织昨天证实，刚果东北部的伊波拉（Ebola）病毒疫情已经失控，正在迅速蔓延扩散，过去1周至少有31人因感染而病发身亡。1976年，在刚果第1次爆发这种疾病，因而取名伊波拉病毒。感染的人类会出现病毒性出血热症状，当时的死亡率高达88%。
sum_content: The Ebola virus epidemic in the northeast of the Congo has been out of control and is spread rapidly. In 1976, the disease broke out for the first time in the Congo, which was named Ipora virus.

content_en: The World Health Organization (WHO) confirmed yesterday that the Ebola virus outbreak in northeastern Congo is out of control and spreading rapidly, with at least 31 people dying from the infection in the past week. In 1976, the first outbreak of the disease occurred in Congo, hence the name Ebola virus. Infected humans develop symptoms of viral hemorrhagic fever, which has a mortality rate of up to 88%.

content: 12月21上午国家版权局、公安部、工信部第八次打击网络盗版专项治理“剑网行动”新闻通气会，针对网络文学、音乐、视频、游戏、动漫、软件和网络销售平台等领域，查办网络侵权盗版案件282件，行政结案210件，移送司法机关72件，关闭侵犯信息网络传播权、未经许可从事互联网视听服务等网站183家。

content: 【让电脑提速的小方法】开始菜单里点击"运行"，输入gpedit.msc指令后确定，会出现一个小屏幕，然后单击计算机配置--管理模板--网络--QoS数据计划程序，选“限制可保留带宽”，“设置”选“已启用”，将“带宽限制”中的20改为0，“应用”，就可以使用100%的网速,因为平时Windows XP自动保留20%的网速。
sum_content: Windows XP automatically retains 20%of the network speed. Change 20 in "bandwidth limit" to 0, "application" can use 100%network speed.

content_en: Click "Small Ways to speed up your Computer" in the Start menu. Run" msc command to confirm, a small screen will appear, and then click Computer Configuration -- Management template -- Network --QoS data scheduler, select "Limit Reserved bandwidth", "Settings" select "Enabled", change 20 in "Bandwidth Limit" to 0, "Apply", "Limit bandwidth" to "Apply". You can use 100% of the Internet speed, because Windows XP automatically retains 20% of the Internet speed.

content: 《土地使用权70年的由来》 1981年10月12日，中山宾馆，香港霍英东向国务院总理周恩来建议搞土地有偿使用。 总理问：土地使用权多少年合适？ 霍回答：按香港惯例，99年。 总理说：那是殖民地。 霍回答：可以定70年。 遂，土地有偿使用期定为70年。
sum_content: Huo Yingdong advised the State Council Premier Zhou Enlai to propose to the land for paid use. According to Hong Kong practice, 99 years.

content_en: "The 70-year History of Land Use Right" October 12, 1981, Zhongshan Hotel, Hong Kong Fok Yingdong suggested to Premier Zhou Enlai to engage in paid use of land. Premier: How many years is the right to use land? Huo replied: According to Hong Kong practice, 99 years. The Prime Minister said: That's a colony. Huo replied: It can be fixed for 70 years. Therefore, the paid use period of land is set at 70 years.

content: 【悼】Lulu——英国海域最后一头虎鲸死亡。人们在苏格兰的Tiree岛上发现了被冲上岸的Lulu的遗体。科学家分析认为，Lulu是在被渔网一类捕鱼工具缠绕后导致死亡的。英国科学家认为这可能宣告了虎鲸在英国海域灭绝。苏格兰水域过去12个月内已经有4头鲸因为缠绕死亡
sum_content: Remains of Lulu rushed ashore on Tiree Island of Scotland. British scientists believe that this may announce the extinction of killer whales in the British waters.
img2txt: blackwhite penguin,graylarge rock,largegraybrown rock,whitesmall wave,largegraybig rock,blackgrayrockywet rock,whitesmall wave,graylargebig rock,whitebluegraycloudy sky,largegraybrowndarksmall rock,a seal on the rocks at the beachcuohnpomanmspe tieeoeedn@eco Chinese website
content_en: Lulu - the last killer whale in British waters has died. Lulu's body was found washed up on the island of Tiree in Scotland. Scientists believe that Lulu died after becoming entangled in fishing tools such as fishing nets. British scientists believe this may have declared killer whales extinct in British waters. Four whales have died from entanglement in Scottish waters in the past 12 months

content: 【地主家穷的只有石油了】俄罗斯央行12月27日起施行货币兑换新规，按照修订第499号《关于金融机构客户身份识别，防止洗钱及恐怖分子融资活动》条例，购买或出售超过15000卢布（约合213美元）需提供护照、注册地址、生日及纳税人识别号，并填写调查问卷。此举旨在防止洗钱及恐怖分子的融资活动。
sum_content: The Russian central bank will implement new currency exchange regulations on December 27. More than 15,000 ruble (about $ 213) must provide a passport, registered address, birthday and taxpayer identification number.
img2txt: largewhitestone building,greenpinetalllarge tree,greentallpineevergreen tree,tallsmallpinegreenevergreen tree,greenpinetalllarge tree,largeglassarched window,largebrownglasstall window,greentallpine tree,walkingstanding woman,redblue flag,a woman standing in front of a building
content_en: The Central Bank of Russia has implemented new currency exchange regulations since December 27, in accordance with the revision of the regulation No. 499 on the Identification of clients of financial institutions to Prevent Money Laundering and terrorist Financing activities, the purchase or sale of more than 15,000 rubles (about $213) must provide a passport, registered address, birthday and taxpayer identification number. And fill out the questionnaire. The move is aimed at preventing money laundering and terrorist financing.

content: 【湖南高三学生办公室内当母亲面杀害班主任】今日早上，湖南邵东县一名学生在办公室内持刀将老师杀害。据悉，被害老师姓腾，49岁，是嫌疑人的班主任。嫌疑人姓龙，高三学生。因考试成绩不理想，被叫了家长。事发时，嫌疑人、嫌疑人母亲及被害人都在教师办公室。目前案件正在调查。O湖南高三学生办公室内当母亲面杀害班主任

content_en: A student in Shaodong County, Hunan province, killed his teacher with a knife in his office this morning. It is reported that the victim surnamed Teng, 49 years old, is the suspect's class teacher. Suspect surnamed Long, high school senior. The parents were called because the exam results were not satisfactory. At the time of the incident, the suspect, the suspect's mother and the victim were in the teacher's office. The case is currently under investigation. O Killing the head teacher in front of his mother in the senior high school office in Hunan Province

content: 【国家运动员张培萌起诉东风悦达】近日，短跑运动员张培萌将东风悦达起亚汽车有限公司告上法庭，索赔31万。其表示该公司在官方微信上擅自将其肖像用于汽车广告宣传，而张培萌是宝马汽车代言人，东风锐达起亚公司的行为影响其正常代言活动，属于侵权。日前，海淀法院受理了此案。（北青报记者 孔德婧）
sum_content: National athlete Zhang Peimeng brought Dongfeng Yueda Kiaqia Automobile Co., Ltd. to court and claimed 310,000. A few days ago, the Haidian Court accepted the case.

content_en: [National athlete Zhang Peimeng sues Dongfeng Yueda] Recently, sprinter Zhang Peimeng took Dongfeng Yueda Kia Motors Co., Ltd. to court, claiming 310,000 yuan. It said that the company used its image in car advertising without authorization on the official wechat, and Zhang Peimeng is the spokesman of BMW, Dongfeng Ruida Kia company's behavior affects its normal endorsement activities, which is an infringement. A few days ago, Haidian court accepted the case. (Kong Dejing, Reporter for Beiqing Daily)
